The '''Caryn Seamount''' is a [[seamount]] in the [[Atlantic Ocean]]. It is an independent seamount located southwest of the [[New England Seamounts]], which was active more than 100 million years ago.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://earthref.org/cgi-bin/sc.cgi?id=SMNT-367N-0680W |title=Seamount Catalog - Caryn Seamount |website=Earthref.org |date= |accessdate=2016-03-04}}</ref>

