'''Tanchowk''' ({{lang-ne|तान्चोक}}) or Tonju ( तोंजु ) in [[Gurung]] language is located in [[Lumle]] VDC,{{Clarify|date=April 2011}} [[Kaski District]] of [[Nepal]]. It is about 45&nbsp;km northwest of [[Pokhara]] and on the way to [[Annapurna]] base camp.

